meta.description:
This build is for epidemiologic purposes, including the surveillance and tracking of the Delta variant (B.1.617.2).  
It is made possible by the sharing of genomic data from Sequencing Labs in Nebraska. We gratefully acknowledge the Sequencing Labs and the authors for the genomic data on which this analysis is based.
Data source: https://www.gisaid.org/
meta.title: Delta variant Genomic Surveillance in Nebraska
